or: #A29BFE;\">🌟 NEW CHALLENGE DETECTED!</h3>\n","            <p>Great job making it this far, <b>{player_name}</b>!</p>\n","            <div style=\"background-color: #2d3436; padding: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #00b894;\">\n","                <p>💡 <b>Coach Analysis:</b> It looks like the <b>[{failed_concept}]</b> concept is putting up a bit of a fight.</p>\n","            </div>\n","            <p><i>Let's take a quick Tactical Pause to recharge this skill before moving on!</i></p>\n","        </div>\n","        \"\"\"\n","\n","# ==========================================\n","# 3. STUDENT INTERFACE: THE \"LEVEL UP\" SCREEN\n","# ==========================================\n","print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*80)\n","print(f\"🎮 PLAYER SCREEN: NEW QUEST FOR {display_name.upper()}\")\n","print(\"=\"*80)\n","\n","# Call the LLM to generate the unique HTML\n","dynamic_dialogue_html = generate_dynamic_gamified_ui(display_name, translated_feature)\n","\n","# Display the LLM-generated UI\n","display(HTML(dynamic_dialogue_html))\n","\n","print(\"\\n[INFO] Dynamic Student interface deployed. Teacher Decision Support moved to Subject 2 Module.\")"],"metadata":{"id":"n_HantrlyIVk","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1775390765356,"user_tz":-60,"elapsed":3724,"user":{"displayName":"Oumaima Méchi","userId":"09875582261966675902"}},"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":489},"outputId":"1b6d2d97-d769-402d-fee2-c70ff66f3efa"},"execution_count":19,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\n","================================================================================\n","🎮 PLAYER SCREEN: NEW QUEST FOR PLAYER #84112\n","================================================================================\n","[WARNING] LLM Generation failed. Deploying standard static UI.\n"]},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stderr","text":["/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/google/colab/_import_hooks/_hook_injector.py:55: FutureWarning: \n","\n","All support for